<section class="section cpf-s3">
  <div class="container">

    <h2 class="cpf-s3__heading">
      Why Chemical Peels Deliver The Most Dramatic Skin Transformation
    </h2>

    <div class="cpf-s3__grid">

      <div class="cpf-s3__card">
        <h3 class="cpf-s3__card-title">Immediate and Long-Term Results</h3>
        <p class="cpf-s3__card-body">You'll see smoother, brighter skin within days of your treatment, with continued improvement for weeks. Chemical peels reduce fine lines by up to 60%, fade dark spots significantly, and improve overall skin texture better than any other single treatment. Most clients see results that last 3-6 months.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cpf-s3__card">
        <h3 class="cpf-s3__card-title">Scientifically Proven Anti-Aging Benefits</h3>
        <p class="cpf-s3__card-body">Chemical peels stimulate natural collagen production and accelerate cell turnover, giving you the skin renewal that typically takes months in just one treatment. This process not only improves current skin issues but helps prevent future aging by resetting your skin's natural regeneration cycle.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cpf-s3__card">
        <h3 class="cpf-s3__card-title">Customizable for Every Skin Concern</h3>
        <p class="cpf-s3__card-body">We offer light, medium, and deep peels tailored to your specific skin issues and tolerance level. Whether you're dealing with acne scars, sun damage, melasma, or just want an overall refresh, we'll select the perfect peel strength and formula to give you optimal results safely.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cpf-s3__card">
        <h3 class="cpf-s3__card-title">Safe and Professional Application</h3>
        <p class="cpf-s3__card-body">Our licensed estheticians are expertly trained in chemical peel application and will monitor your skin throughout the entire process. We use only medical-grade peels and follow strict safety protocols to ensure you get maximum results with minimal risk of complications or uneven healing.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

